ges/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FinkAvenue</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Ousted <strong>Intel Corporation</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) CEO Pat Gelsinger was in the news asking for people to \u201cpray(ing) and fast(ing) for the 100K Intel employees as they navigate this difficult period,\u201d The company's share price is down more than 20% after tough news</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743045-pray-and-fast-for-intel", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 18:44:02"}, {"id": "4743043", "title": "Why Lockheed Martin Stock Is A Buy In 2025 Despite Low Growth", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/465513294/image_465513294.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"F-35 Lightning Stealth Jet Landing at 2015 Yuma Air Show\" data-id=\"465513294\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/465513294/image_4